<HEADLINE> Jimenez Wins Sixth Stage in Tour of Spain Cycle Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Spain's Jose Maria Jimenez of
the Banesto team on Thursday won the 201.5-kilometer sixth stage
of the Tour of Spain cycle race from Murcia to Xorret del Cati.
</P>
<P>
Jimenez broke away in the closing kilometers during the ascent
of the col de Cati, the first serious climb in the race.
</P>
