existing bilateral accord signed five years ago. He hailed the
excellent cooperation between Cyprus and Israel in health area in
the past years.
</P>
<P>
Cyprus' relations with Israel have been greatly enhanced since
the opening of its embassy in Tel Aviv five years ago and through
the exchange of visits by high-ranking officials.
</P>
