SPH topped the gainers of the day as it moved up 40 cents to
close at 13.30 Singapore dollars. Apac Brew moved up 19 cents to
finish at 3.04 Singapore dollars. ChemInd w02 inched up 13 cents
to end 0.25 Singapore dollars.
</P>
<P>
