commercial and property development, professional management and
consultancy and financial services.
</P>
<P>
Rafidah's mission will include Pulau Pinang Chief Minister Koh
Tsu Koon, state officials from states of Johor, Perak and
Terengganu and 24 representatives from 16 companies, the
statement said. 
