<HEADLINE> Internet Boosts Peony Exports </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZHENGZHOU, September 11 (Xinhua) -- A company in suburban
Luoyang in central China's Henan Province recently exported 1,350
peony stems worth about 100,000 yuan to northern European
countries.
